</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-xiLah hUMvDY pf-24_ pf-text-1"><strong>Impact on survival rates</strong> - Less than 1 in 10 people survive an out-of-hospital cardiac arrest in the UK. However, if CPR is initiated early, the survival rates can increase significantly.



























